The paper deals with side-channel analysis, which is a subfield of computer security (cs.CR). The use of unsupervised learning techniques such as LSTM auto-encoders and MLP networks suggests that the paper may also fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves the use of cryptographic algorithms, which could place it under the category of cryptography (cs.CY). Additionally, the paper deals with hardware implementations of AES, which could place it under the category of computer architecture (cs.AR) or software engineering (cs.SE).
